Global Hospital Linen Market Insights
Hospital Linen Market size was valued at USD 8.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 12.3 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Hospital Linen Market Overview
The global hospital linen market was valued at USD 11.89 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 18.14 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.1% during the forecast period. The hospital linen market includes products such as bed sheets, towels, blankets, surgical drapes, and gowns, which are critical for maintaining hygiene and safety standards in healthcare facilities. The increasing demand for healthcare services, particularly in the wake of the global health crisis, has led to a rise in hospital admissions, driving the need for medical linens. Additionally, growing awareness about patient safety and hygiene is contributing to market growth.

